discussiontools-preference-description:
Tobbiyo sinttaa mali be'uwaa eeshshata ootissees:
* [https
://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Talk_pages_project/Usability Show metadata meetaa daataa] ooratta tobbetanne ooratta sinttaa utettaa ootissees.
*[https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Talk_pages_project/  Ooratta tobbiyaa Ooratta huuphe yohota gujja] garssa yafaraa go'ettiyoogan.
* Ooratta qofati ne xaafettido kifiliya gujettiyoode [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Talk_pages_project/  erissota ekka].
* Issi issi tobbiyaabaanne ooratta sinttaa utettaa ootissanawu [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Talk_pages_project/  Go'ettana danddayettiyaagaa meetaa daatan bessa].
{{GENDER:|Ne}} [[Special:Preferences#mw-prefsection-editing-discussion|doorota]] meeziyan go'ettanawu danddayaasa.

Ooraxissoti [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Talk_pages_project/ proojektiyaa oraxissuwaa sinttan] wodhoosona. 

Hayyanaa hassaya:
* Wodiyaappe guyyiyan ooratta mali be'o eeshshati gujettoosona.
* Qommon de'iya amarida eeshshati ne wikkiiyan hanno gaakkanawu waayi de'ana.
